messages.subject: I'm done, too
messages.msgSnippet: I have been a member of this list for quite a few years, now, and I, too, have been waiting for this nonsense to die down and it seems like it s not going to.
messages.messageBody:
I have been a member of this list for quite a few years, now, and I,
too, have been waiting for this nonsense to die down and it seems
like it's not going to. Fine. I'm gone. I don't need this
negative energy in my life.

Get over yourselves, already. Sheesh.

Janet
